  "projectDescription": "This autonomous wheeled robot monitors power line corridors using a high-resolution thermal imager to detect electrical faults. Controlled by a Raspberry Pi with 5G connectivity, the 12V differential-drive chassis utilizes an aluminum frame and weatherproof housing for rugged, real-time remote inspection.",
